public abstract class ImmutableAccessor<T extends org.springframework.jdbc.core.namedparam.NamedParameterJdbcOperations,P extends org.springframework.jdbc.core.namedparam.SqlParameterSource>
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingCollection<T>
implements DataSourceAccessor<T,P>

Abstract accessor implementation as a wrapper around provided collection. Copies provided collection into inner immutable one on creation. Thread-safe.

alexkasko Date: 6/11/12
